247
00:25:26,208 --> 00:25:27,501
Joder.

248
00:25:27,583 --> 00:25:28,834
Está bien. Sal de aquí.

249
00:25:31,166 --> 00:25:33,084
- Hay que darle vuelta.
- ¡Suéltenme!

250
00:25:33,166 --> 00:25:34,209
Apártate.

251
00:25:54,250 --> 00:25:55,876
<i>En 1922...</i>

252
00:25:58,375 --> 00:25:59,959
