257
00:26:21,708 --> 00:26:24,251
<i>por las razones
que este documento mostrará.</i>

258
00:26:35,625 --> 00:26:36,625
De acuerdo.

259
00:26:36,791 --> 00:26:38,001
Sólo un poco más.

260
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:41,584
Eso no es una tumba.

261
00:26:41,916 --> 00:26:43,667
- No para mamá.
- Muchacho.

262
00:26:47,166 --> 00:26:48,166
Henry.

263
00:26:49,041 --> 00:26:50,041
Henry.

264
00:26:55,333 --> 00:26:56,333
Muchacho.

